This is a Next.js project with Polkadot API (PAPI) and KheopsKit wallet integration.

For any major code changes, follow the @ui.mdc rules to ensure best practices are maintained.

## Testing Changes with pnpm dev

When implementing changes or fixes, always test them using the development server:
- Check if the server is already running on the default port (3000) 
- If the development server is not running on 3000, run `pnpm dev` to start the Next.js development server


